OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FA 94-year-old woman died after being
OL,7,Fhit by an advertising board near the
OL,8,FGrand Pier in Weston-super-Mare, a
OL,9,Fhearing has been told.
OL,11,FMargaret Carter, of Lydney,
OL,12,FGloucestershire, died on 28 October
OL,13,F2021 after one of the pier's
OL,14,Fadvertising boards - which weighed
OL,15,Fmore than 100 kilograms - was blown
OL,16,Fover by a strong gust of wind,
OL,17,Fknocking her down.
OL,19,FShe had been walking on the promenade
OL,20,Fat the time.
