OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FMrs Carter waited three hours in
OL,7,Fterrible weather for an ambulance, and
OL,8,Fdied after eventually being taken by
OL,9,Fhelicopter to Southmead Hospital in
OL,10,FBristol.
OL,12,FIn a single hearing at North Somerset
OL,13,FMagistrates Court on Friday, the court
OL,14,Fheard that there would have been a
OL,15,F"high risk of death" for an elderly
OL,16,Fperson struck by the board even if
OL,17,Fmedical attention had been received
OL,18,Fsooner.
