OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FSusan Jane Firman, one of Mrs Carter's
OL,7,Fdaughters, said in her victim
OL,8,Fstatement: "The most difficult thing
OL,9,Fat the time was that she must have
OL,10,Fbeen in so much pain."
OL,12,FThe court heard it was up to the
OL,13,Fjudgement of Grand Pier staff as to
OL,14,Fwhether it was too windy for the large
OL,15,FA-boards to be out on the promenade.
