OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FAt the time of the incident, Grand
OL,7,FPier Ltd - the company which owns and
OL,8,Fruns the attraction - had not
OL,9,Fappointed a competent person
OL,10,Fresponsible for health and safety, in
OL,11,Fcontravention of health and safety
OL,12,Fregulations.
OL,14,FThe company pleaded guilty to a
OL,15,Ffailure to discharge general health
OL,16,Fand safety duty to a person other than
OL,17,Fan employee, and contravening a health
OL,18,Fand safety regulation.
