OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FIt was fined #133,200, and ordered to
OL,7,Fpay costs of #61,187.84, and a #190
OL,8,Fsurcharge.
OL,10,FIn the sentencing, the company's
OL,11,Fdefence - which opened by expressing
OL,12,Fits "sorrow" for Mrs Carter's death
OL,13,Fand apologising to the family - argued
OL,14,Fit only had a "medium culpability" for
OL,15,Fthe tragedy so should face a lower
OL,16,Ffine.
