OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Angela Brereton found
OL,7,Fthat Grand Pier Ltd had a high
OL,8,Fculpability for the accident and
OL,9,Fimposed a fine towards the top end of
OL,10,Fthe guidance amount.
OL,12,FShe warned that the health and safety
OL,13,Fsystems in place were "clearly not
OL,14,Fadequate" and that employees did not
OL,15,Fhave adequate training.
OL,17,FShe said: "The offence exposed a
OL,18,Fnumber of members of the public to the
OL,19,Frisk of harm due to the number of
OL,20,Fvisitors through the year."
