OL,3,C'Wonderful' mum, 94, died after being
OL,4,Cstruck by seafront advertising board
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Brereton said: "The
OL,7,Fbreach of health and safety laws will
OL,8,Fnot be tolerated and I greatly hope
OL,9,Fyou will stop anything like this
OL,10,Fhappening again."
OL,12,FThe A-boards themselves have not been
OL,13,Fused since the accident. They were
OL,14,Fseized by North Somerset Council and
OL,15,FGrand Pier Ltd told the court they did
OL,16,Fnot want them back.
